description: Exceptional 3 bedroom, 2 bath condominium situated in a highly sought after South Boston neighborhood. This well appointed building is centrally located within walking distance of the Seaport, East/West Broadway, Castle Island and is on the very desirable West First St corridor. The interior finishes in this dramatic condominium will exceed your every expectation: Stylish Chef’s kitchen with a professional grade Viking appliance package including direct venting hoods, custom cabinets, quartz counter tops, spa like baths, hardwood floors, separate laundry room, great ceiling height, large windows, excellent natural light and a spectacular roof deck with amazing views. This building has been professionally designed and offers tastefully finished common areas, elevator access and garage parking. This property is truly one of South Boston's finest developments combining striking architecture and a phenomenal location.
